    "summary": "Experienced management consultant and program / project manager. Focus areas:\n* Corporate, international companies;\n* Strategic sourcing and outsourcing;\n* Inspire Confidence. Empower Change;\n* Transformation, Change Management, Getting things done.\n\nWorked at strategy firm to see the bigger picture; worked at operational firms to get hands dirty.\nWorked on the ground in a variety of countries (including Denmark, France, Germany, Italy, Japan, Russia, Sweden, Switzerland, United Kingdom) and with many more nationalities to understand the importance of communication and culture.\nWorked at well reputed firms (including Adecco, Akzo Nobel, ING, Philips, T-Mobile,T-Systems, UPC, Vattenfall, VimpelCom and Volvo) to understand complex decison making processes.\nWorked in many different settings to understand the difference between management and leadership.\nWorked in many complex and turbulent situations to understand what it takes to get the job done.\n\nSpecialties: business transformation, organization change management, (strategic) sourcing, project leadership, RFX management, translation of strategies into actionable action plans.",
